overview:
Paxum Inc is a Canadian Incorporated company, registered with FINTRAC as a Money Services Business. Offering Global Payroll solutions, a prepaid Mastercard for every account, and easy access to funds, Paxum provides a low-cost alternative to traditional payroll methods.

International clients are very welcome, with only a few countries restricted. Bulk payments, Pay Now buttons, Set fees (rather than percentages), Instant Access to funds, and payment privacy are just some of the key features and benefits of Paxum Ewallet Payment Services.

Paxum welcomes clients of all types and from the majority of business sectors. Find out for yourself just how easy it is to get setup with a free account so you can instantly send and receive money online by contacting Paxum today!
